structures.trees.auxiliary

Class BinaryTree.BinaryTreeIterator<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • structures.trees.auxiliary.BinaryTree.BinaryTreeIterator<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Generic type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<T>
    Enclosing interface:
    BinaryTree<T>

    public static class BinaryTree.BinaryTreeIterator<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<T>
    Basic iterator for iterating over BinaryTree in order, essentially, the BinaryTree is converted to an ArrayList, and then traversed with the ArrayList's iterator. This is not space effective, or time effective, but it keeps the code a lot simpler
